# FSD in @wish/web

When editing `apps/web`, follow Feature-Sliced Design (adapted). Full guide: `.cursor/skills/fsd-web-feature/SKILL.md`.

## Layers

```
apps/web/src/
тФЬтФАтФА app/[locale]/     # Routes only тАФ thin page.tsx, layouts, route CSS
тФЬтФАтФА core/
тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА app/          # Shell: MainLayout, Providers, RootBody
тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА widgets/      # Composite blocks: Header, Footer
тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА features/     # User actions: auth, languageSelector
тФВ   тФФтФАтФА shared/       # Cross-cutting: router, utils (no UI features)
тФФтФАтФА i18n/             # next-intl config (not an FSD layer)
```

## Import direction (strict)

| From | May import |
| ---- | ---------- |
| `app/` | `core/*`, `@wish/ui-kit`, `@/i18n/*` |
| `widgets/` | `features/`, `shared/`, `@wish/ui-kit` |
| `features/` | `shared/`, `@wish/ui-kit` |
| `shared/` | external libs only |

**Forbidden:** `features/` тЖТ `widgets/`; `shared/` тЖТ `features/` or `widgets/`; `core/*` тЖТ `app/`; `@wish/ui-kit` тЖТ anything from `apps/web`.

## Where to add code

- **New user flow / action** тЖТ `core/features/<name>/` with `index.ts` public API (`hooks/`, `ui/`, `api/`, `context/` as needed)
- **Large composed block** (header, footer) тЖТ `core/widgets/<name>/`
- **New route** тЖТ `app/[locale]/.../page.tsx` тАФ delegate UI to `core/features` or `core/widgets`; use `(main-layout)` when header/footer needed
- **Reusable primitive** тЖТ `@wish/ui-kit`, not copied into web
- **Do not** add new code under legacy `src/components/` тАФ use `core/features` or `core/widgets`

## Conventions

- Navigation: `@/i18n/navigation` (`Link`, `useRouter`) тАФ not `next/link` / `next/navigation` directly
- Route constants: extend `core/shared/router/routes.ts`
- `'use client'` only where hooks/events are needed; keep pages server when possible
- App-specific styles: `*.module.css` in `core/`; route CSS next to `page.tsx`; do not duplicate ui-kit component styles
- Strings: next-intl locale files тАФ no hardcoded user-visible copy in components

## Examples

```tsx
// тЬЕ app/[locale]/auth/page.tsx тАФ thin page
import { LoginForm } from '@/core/features/auth';

export default function AuthPage() {
  return <LoginForm />;
}

// тЭМ feature importing a widget
import { Header } from '@/core/widgets/header/Header';

// тЭМ business logic + markup directly in page.tsx (belongs in core/features)
```

## Verify after changes

```bash
pnpm --filter @wish/web lint
pnpm --filter @wish/web test:run
```
